    <p>SHEETS: I just had to get this length off so I could look presentable when I go in.</p>
    <p>WANG: Looking presentable has been a challenge at home, where Sheets' family had been living days without safe tap water.</p>
    <p>SHEETS: Had to drive to a truck stop - $13 a shower.</p>
    <p>WANG: Sheets eventually found free showers at St. Francis Church in a small town nearby, St. Albans, where the water supply has been fine. And business these past few days has been even better.</p>
    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF COINS)</p>
