<h1> "Job Vacant After Karachi's Top Counter-Terrorism Cop Is Killed" </h1>
    <p>DAVID GREENE, HOST: </p>
    <p>Taliban militants have been expanding their operations in Pakistan. They're better known for attacks in the rural mountains, but they're also active in the cities of that populous country.</p>
    <p>STEVE INSKEEP, HOST: </p>
